description: Filled with flavoursome goodies like sweet potato, crumbled beef sausage, spinach and parmesan, make this delicious frittata recipe in just 20 minutes.
keywords: Beef Sausage, Spinach & Sweet Potato Bake
name: Beef Sausage, Spinach & Sweet Potato Bake Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 Woolworths beef sausage with roasted garlic & parsley

recipeInstructions.text: Whisk eggs and milk together in a small jug. Season. Add sweet potato mixture to pan and stir gently to combine. Add egg mixture and stir to combine. Cook for 3 minutes, without stirring, or until almost set. Sprinkle over half of the cheese. Grill for 2 minutes or until set. Serve topped with remaining spinach and cheese.
